      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Here's a great opportunity to get into a reliable, well-kept vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been thoughtfully maintained and is ready to serve you well on the road. You'll find the mechanicals are sound and dependable, with only the expected minor cosmetic wear that comes from regular, everyday use. No nasty surprises here \u2014 just a honest, capable car at a fair price. Come take it for a spin!",
