    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, drivable vehicle that gets the job done? This car might be just what you need! It's in fair condition \u2014 fully functional and ready to drive, though it does show some noticeable wear both inside and out that you'd expect from a vehicle at this stage of its life. There may be some cosmetic blemishes and minor imperfections, but the mechanicals are working and it's a solid option for a budget-conscious buyer. A great opportunity to get on the road without breaking the bank!",
      "price": 20000.0,
