      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's a solid budget-friendly opportunity for the practical buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's been around the block and shows it, with visible wear on the interior and exterior and a few minor mechanical quirks to be aware of. That said, it's a functional, drivable car that can serve you well with some TLC. If you're looking to save money upfront and don't mind putting in a little work, this could be a great fit!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, dependable car that strikes an excellent balance between value and quality. The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with normal use, such as light surface scratches or small door dings, but nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but free from major stains or damage. Mechanically, the car runs and drives confidently, with no known issues \u2014 it has been properly maintained and is ready for everyday use without requiring immediate repairs. This is a solid, honest vehicle for a buyer who wants reliability and good presentation without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in genuinely mint condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you about what that means. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels are straight and true. The interior is equally impressive, with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim pieces; everything looks and feels as though it has been meticulously cared for from day one. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and all mechanical systems are functioning exactly as they should, with no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises. This is the kind of used car that is genuinely difficult to find \u2014 one where you don't have to make compromises or budget for immediate repairs or cosmetic fixes. A full service history is available, and we encourage any interested buyer to arrange an independent inspection \u2014 we are confident it will confirm everything described here.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
